function rout = RateMichMenLin(spikes,p)% RateMichMen: Michaelis-Menten model for firing rate to a square pulse of ligand% rout = RateMichMen(spikes,p), where the parameters p are%	p(1) = spont. firing rate%	p(2) = const. of proportionality btw. rate & active fraction%		(i.e. rate = p(2)*(active fraction) + p(1))%	p(3) = on rate prefactor (mult. by conc.)%	p(4) = off rate%	p(5) = duration of ligand application%	p(6) = time delay%	p(7) = concentrationpnew = p(1:6);pnew(3) = p(3)*p(7);rout = RateMichMen(spikes,pnew);